      "writtenOn": "2026-03-25T11:00:55Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Actually this case is handled by the refresh flow introduced in another commit.\n\nWhen a property like Resolved is updated on BMC A and synced to BMC B, the corresponding file change triggers the refresh path (refreshFromDisk), which updates the in-memory entry on the peer.\nhttps://gerrit.openbmc.org/c/openbmc/phosphor-logging/+/88590",
      "parentUuid": "2551700d_d580f217",
