      "message": "Also, will `inotifyFD` \u0026 `errDirWatcherWD` makes more sense? \n\nReasos for suggestion :\n\ninotifyFD --\u003e It\u0027s an inotify instance (actually a FD), but can setup multiple path watches, so generic could be better.\n\nerrDirWatcherWD --\u003e we are watching the error directory, rather than individual files inside.",
